==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Precedential
<hw>Prec`e*den"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the nature
of a precedent; having force as an example for imitation; <as>as,
<ex>precedential</ex> transactions</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All their actions in that time are not <qex>precedential</qex> to
warrant posterity.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Precedently</ent>⟦br⟧
